net.hypixel.skyblock.util

Class MithrilPowderCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hypixel.skyblock.util.MithrilPowderCalculator

  • @Immutable
public final class MithrilPowderCalculator
extends java.lang.Object
    Calculates how much Mithril Powder an upgrade for HOTM costs.
    More information can be found here.
    Most methods should have a level being upgraded to as input.
    All methods should return an integer cost of Mithril Powder.
    Since:
    15 January 2021
    Version:
    27 July 2021
    Author:
    MrPineapple070
